title: Bug 121170 - get column label from meta data object should return some user recognizable strings
OB: When retrieving the column labels from the meta data object, the labels are currently null. However, after extraction, the labels are replaced with recognizable strings.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Access the meta data object.
2. Retrieve the column labels.
3. Compare the retrieved labels with the recognizable strings after extraction.
